    stem: 'An 8-year-old student who has been wearing bilateral hearing aids since age 2 demonstrates the following speech pattern: consistent distortion of /s, z, sh, ch, j/ (high-frequency fricatives and affricates) despite adequate aided thresholds through 4000 Hz. The SLP should implement:',
