      c: 'Phone avoidance related to stuttering is within SLP scope. The SLP should integrate cognitive-affective components into stuttering treatment, collaborating with psychology if needed but not abdicating the communication focus.',
      d: 'A naturalness rating of 6/9 (with 9 being most natural) shows improvement from baseline and indicates reasonable technique use. The issue is the persistent avoidance, not technique quality.',
